<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 06:07:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>俄罗斯城市因洪水上涨呼吁大规模疏散</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-city-calls-for-mass-evacuations-due-to-due-to-rising-flood-waters/articleshow/109262390.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109262390.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于积雪融化导致洪水汹涌，奥伦堡和库尔干当局发出紧急疏散电话。超过10万人从哈萨克斯坦撤离。乌拉尔河泛滥，导致12万人流离失所。萨尔明市长敦促做好准备。俄罗斯和哈萨克斯坦的房屋和基础设施面临的威胁不断升级。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 04:45:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-city-calls-for-mass-evacuations-due-to-due-to-rising-flood-waters/articleshow/109262390.cms</guid></item><item><title>联邦法官驳回亨特·拜登驳回枪支指控的动议</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/federal-judge-denies-hunter-bidens-motion-to-dismiss-gun-charges/articleshow/109262120.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109262120.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;特拉华州的一名联邦法官拒绝了亨特·拜登驳回对他的枪支指控的请求，为六月份可能的审判铺平了道路。美国地区法官玛丽莲·诺雷卡驳回了拜登的论点，即该案具有政治动机，根据之前的认罪协议，他享有免于起诉的豁免权，并且任命美国检察官大卫·韦斯为特别检察官是不适当的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 04:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/federal-judge-denies-hunter-bidens-motion-to-dismiss-gun-charges/articleshow/109262120.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国：中国正在加强俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争机器</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/china-is-strengthening-russias-war-machine-in-ukraine-us/articleshow/109261171.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109261171.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据报道，中国通过提供无人机和导弹技术、卫星图像和机床来支持俄罗斯在乌克兰的军事行动。尽管中国大使馆予以否认，拜登总统还是向习近平主席提出了这个问题。这项援助填补了俄罗斯国防生产的关键缺口，帮助莫斯科进行军事扩张。美国官员强调，停止中国的支持对于援助乌克兰至关重要。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 03:07:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/china-is-strengthening-russias-war-machine-in-ukraine-us/articleshow/109261171.cms</guid></item><item><title>“世界需要美国......”：日本首相岸田敦促美国克服对全球领导力的“自我怀疑”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-needs-us-to-japanese-pm-kishida-urges-us-to-overcome-self-doubt-about-global-leadership/articleshow/109262073.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109262073.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本首相岸田强调美国领导力的重要性，并对美国人对其全球角色的自我怀疑表示担忧。他将对乌克兰的支持与阻止中国的侵略联系起来，强调中国的军事行动对全球和平的威胁。岸田呼吁团结一致承认中国是一个重大威胁，这在国会中引起了跨党派的共鸣。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 04:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/world-needs-us-to-japanese-pm-kishida-urges-us-to-overcome-self-doubt-about-global-leadership/articleshow/109262073.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国气候变化大臣格雷厄姆·斯图尔特辞职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-climate-change-minister-graham-stuart-resigns/articleshow/109260701.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109260701.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;英国气候变化大臣格雷厄姆·斯图尔特在任职八年后辞去政府职务，称辞职时机已到。由于工党在民意调查中领先，斯图尔特计划与首相里希·苏纳克的保守党一起竞选连任。贾斯汀·汤姆林森接替斯图尔特担任气候部长，承认斯图尔特对清洁能源转型的贡献。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 02:19:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-climate-change-minister-graham-stuart-resigns/articleshow/109260701.cms</guid></item><item><title>无政府状态的海地终于成立过渡统治委员会</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/transitional-ruling-council-finally-forms-in-anarchic-haiti/articleshow/109260249.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109260249.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;星期五，这个加勒比国家正式成立了一个管理委员会，其任务是填补海地的领导真空并恢复表面上的秩序，该国受到帮派暴力爆发的冲击。该法令要求理事会“迅速”任命新总理和“包容”海地各政治派别的政府。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/transitional-ruling-council-finally-forms-in-anarchic-haiti/articleshow/109260249.cms</guid></item><item><title>关注中国：乔·拜登誓言保卫日本和菲律宾</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/eye-on-china-joe-biden-vows-to-defend-japan-philippines/articleshow/109260067.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109260067.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统拜登重申了对日本和菲律宾的防务承诺，警告不要在南中国海发动袭击。北京为其行为辩护，反对干涉集团政治和损害战略利益的行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Apr 2024 00:00:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/eye-on-china-joe-biden-vows-to-defend-japan-philippines/articleshow/109260067.cms</guid></item><item><title>反军政府部队占领缅甸主要贸易城镇，反攻迫在眉睫</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/anti-junta-forces-take-key-trading-town-in-myanmar-counteroffensive-looms/articleshow/109260019.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109260019.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;抵抗力量占领了泰国边境的重要城镇妙瓦迪，影响了与缅甸的贸易。随着政权计划反攻，数千人逃离。由于担心边境暴力，泰国主动提出调解冲突。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/anti-junta-forces-take-key-trading-town-in-myanmar-counteroffensive-looms/articleshow/109260019.cms</guid></item><item><title>英国向海外提供的援助减少，而用于收容难民的预算却相同</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sending-less-aid-overseas-as-same-budget-used-to-fund-hosting-refugees/articleshow/109259944.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109259944.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2023年，英国将三分之一的援助预算用于收容英国境内的难民，导致发展中国家的资金紧张。对较贫穷国家的双边援助减少，特别是在亚洲，影响了全球支持举措和人道主义援助工作。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/uk-sending-less-aid-overseas-as-same-budget-used-to-fund-hosting-refugees/articleshow/109259944.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙家庭 60 多名成员在以色列多次袭击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109259784.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109259784.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙的塔巴蒂比家庭面临一个月内的第二场悲剧，60 多名亲属在以色列轰炸中丧生。罢工袭击了建筑物，造成 25 人死亡，然后在准备斋月餐食期间造成 36 人死亡。随着损失的加深，家人陷入哀悼。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109259784.cms</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫高级将领对驻以色列美军人员实施旅行限制</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/travel-curbs-on-us-personnel-in-israel-top-general-in-tel-aviv/articleshow/109259701.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109259701.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于伊朗的潜在威胁，美国发布了以色列旅行指南。预计伊朗将发动重大袭击。英国建议公民离开。法国从伊朗撤离外交官家属。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:30:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/travel-curbs-on-us-personnel-in-israel-top-general-in-tel-aviv/articleshow/109259701.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列准备在 48 小时内应对伊朗的潜在袭击：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-bracing-for-potential-attack-from-iran-within-48-hours-report/articleshow/109259649.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109259649.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列为伊朗可能袭击政府目标做好准备。开斋节后紧张局势升级。美国做好防御准备。外交努力加大。报复行动有待德黑兰批准。阿亚图拉阿里·哈梅内伊誓言惩罚以色列。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 23:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-bracing-for-potential-attack-from-iran-within-48-hours-report/articleshow/109259649.cms</guid></item><item><title>爱尔兰新总理表示距离承认巴勒斯坦国“更近了”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/new-irish-pm-says-getting-much-closer-to-recognising-palestinian-state/articleshow/109255552.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255552.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:48:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/new-irish-pm-says-getting-much-closer-to-recognising-palestinian-state/articleshow/109255552.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国称地中海船只倾覆 45 名移民失踪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/un-says-45-migrants-missing-after-boat-capsizes-in-mediterranean/articleshow/109255465.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255465.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;意大利海岸警卫队周三表示，在另一起沉船事故中，已发现 9 具遇难者尸体，并救起 22 人，其中 15 人疑似失踪。幸存者被带到附近的意大利兰佩杜萨岛，这是许多寻求到达欧盟的移民的第一个停靠港。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:42:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/un-says-45-migrants-missing-after-boat-capsizes-in-mediterranean/articleshow/109255465.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯因部长“不可接受”言论召见法国大使</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-summons-french-ambassador-over-ministers-unacceptable-comments/articleshow/109255410.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109255410.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 17:39:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-summons-french-ambassador-over-ministers-unacceptable-comments/articleshow/109255410.cms</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，到 2050 年，日本独居老年人口将增加 47%</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japans-elderly-population-living-alone-to-jump-47-by-2050-research/articleshow/109254665.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109254665.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japans-elderly-population-living-alone-to-jump-47-by-2050-research/articleshow/109254665.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗袭击威胁使该地区紧张，以色列袭击加沙</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-pounds-gaza-as-iran-attack-threat-puts-region-on-edge/articleshow/109254496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109254496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;居民报告周五以色列在加沙中部猛烈开火，伊朗威胁要对本月在叙利亚发动的袭击造成两名伊朗将军死亡，导致地区紧张局势加剧。哈马斯统治地区当局报告称，加沙中部地区发生了数十次新的空袭。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 16:34:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-pounds-gaza-as-iran-attack-threat-puts-region-on-edge/articleshow/109254496.cms</guid></item><item><title>白宫称伊朗对以色列的威胁“真实”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-threat-to-israel-real-says-white-house/articleshow/109253312.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109253312.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;白宫承认伊朗在叙利亚袭击后对以色列发出威胁。柯比确保防御准备状态。阿亚图拉发誓要进行惩罚，内塔尼亚胡则表示已做好准备。德黑兰批评联合国保持沉默，内塔尼亚胡誓言进行报复。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iranian-threat-to-israel-real-says-white-house/articleshow/109253312.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙家庭 60 多名成员在以色列多次袭击中丧生</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109253253.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109253253.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙的塔巴蒂比一家在不到一个月的时间里第二次陷入哀悼，此前以色列对他们避难的建筑物进行了多次轰炸，造成 60 多名亲属死亡。 - “我们在里面时”房屋遭到轰炸 - 塔巴蒂比一家多次因以色列的轰炸而流离失所，他们已经陷入了哀悼之中。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 15:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/over-60-members-of-gaza-family-killed-in-separate-israeli-strikes/articleshow/109253253.cms</guid></item><item><title>联合国专家谴责巴基斯坦强迫婚姻和少数群体改变宗教信仰</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/un-experts-condemn-forced-marriages-religious-conversions-of-minorities-in-pakistan/articleshow/109252208.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109252208.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国专家周四表示，巴基斯坦宗教少数群体的妇女和儿童很容易遭受强迫宗教皈依和婚姻，以及性侵犯和贩运。声明还敦促巴基斯坦当局平等对待所有妇女，包括来自“印度教和基督教”社区的妇女。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 14:39:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/un-experts-condemn-forced-marriages-religious-conversions-of-minorities-in-pakistan/articleshow/109252208.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>